05742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b05a01184e341d29869bb66e66ba74470d06b40","tid":1590414,"uid":44815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請善用不推文模式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77011f0276410bdaf132eb2643f194e2b5adfcc7","tid":1590414,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d822e8eae3ac651df51872135bf74b22cd9ff756","tid":1590414,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"幾時有人可以打救我 守護我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"做0仔? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1044cf91cac0ced82f807381e518dcbd9ea8b93a","tid":1590414,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:33:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"248df583e20fe8e4ec079dfa265237a701bd1264","tid":1590414,"uid":157913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T21:51:20.000Z","msg":"發覺人生總有幾個時期係衰野一齊黎 通常係屋企人/戀人/事業學業/健康 問題排山倒海 <br />\n但總會過 過咗之後你會比之前成長更多 更堅強 更幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共勉之"},{"pid":"ca1446cc75015a4598003f2866ee15c4d587abca","tid":1590414,"uid":224885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"食多d屎"},{"pid":"db0709d8c201292bfb68b95839e3e61c1545c4ea","tid":1590414,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obvGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=1d75b136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係<br />\n過去個兩個月正正常常係比應屆DSE同學仔溫書休息既<br />\n可惜呢個政府搞到大家奉獻左成個暑假，為左自己又好，為左將來又好，為左下一代又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有見連登上有多個關於網上問功課谷既需求，有見及此就有呢個DSE支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，免費網上問功課谷一直以唔張揚嘅方法存在。谷內有十多位Tutors (當中包括現職老師及名校畢業生在讀生)同DSE同學仔。形式係以分科細谷你問我答為主，亦有提供簡單練習同改文服務。同學亦可以問升學選科等問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直隱姓埋名係為左保障學生安全。但見到需求增加，又多左好多不同既補習post。所以我地希望提供俾同學多一個安全安心既選擇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有同學有需要，請聯絡：<br />\nTG: mama612<br />\n(暫時有足夠Tutor所以暫不接受更多tutor)<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}